      <title>印度关系受损 孟加拉国考虑深化与中国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/bangladesh-eyes-deeper-ties-with-china-as-india-relations-suffer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与印度关系依然紧张的当下，孟加拉国正计划与中国和其他东亚经济体建立更加紧密的经济联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/bangladesh-eyes-deeper-ties-with-china-as-india-relations-suffer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 13:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
