      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:44:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国债券发售需求创纪录 长期缺席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/france-offers-bonds-via-banks-for-first-time-in-eight-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国新政府试图争取足够的政治支持来通过急需的预算，该国八个月以来首次银团债券发售获得了前所未有的大量投资者需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/france-offers-bonds-via-banks-for-first-time-in-eight-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚极右翼候选人在动荡后仍保持领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/pro-russian-candidate-leads-romanian-poll-ahead-of-may-ballot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，罗马尼亚极右翼候选人赢得总统选举首轮，震惊政界，目前他依然保持领先地位，当局计划在 5 月份重复竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/pro-russian-candidate-leads-romanian-poll-ahead-of-may-ballot</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 08:15:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普继续威胁征收关税，大宗商品价格回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对墨西哥和加拿大发出关税威胁，再次引发贸易战担忧，石油和工业金属价格下跌，而黄金价格则因投资者寻求避险资产而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 23:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普助推股市和美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员选择关注唐纳德·特朗普总统领导下的经济增长和企业利润前景，美国股指期货、美国国债和美元均上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 22:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
